            Koleksi tools developer sederhana yang berjalan sepenuhnya di browser (Client-Side). Aman, cepat, dan tanpa upload data ke server.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/kandarlubis31" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 dark:hover:text-slate-300 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:-translate-y-0.5" data-i18n="footer.github">Github</a>
            <a href="https://paklubis.my.id" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 dark:hover:text-slate-300 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:-translate-y-0.5" data-i18n="footer.website">Website</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4" data-i18n="footer.categories">Kategori Tools</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li><a href="/pdf" class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-sky-600 dark:hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors" data-i18n="footer.pdf_tools">PDF Tools</a></li>
            <li><a href="/image" class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-sky-600 dark:hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors" data-i18n="footer.image_tools">Image Tools</a></li>
            <li><a href="/dev" class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-sky-600 dark:hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors" data-i18n="footer.dev_tools">Developer Tools</a></li>
          </ul>
